      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNEQUALLED (1) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 27.74 beating Gouda Monelli. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from five starts. Looks the one to beat. SUNSET PARIS (2) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 4th (28.08) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Key player if finds best. DODGY BEAR (4) has a terrific record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from five starts. Recorded a 0.8 lengths win (27.80) in a Novice race last time at this track. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. CANYA BYPASS (5) will give backers a sight.",
